controlinterface.swinguiadvanced.control

Class SwingSimpleControlWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • controlinterface.swinguiadvanced.control.SwingSimpleControlWrapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GeneralEventListener

    public class SwingSimpleControlWrapper
extends java.lang.Object
implements GeneralEventListener
    Provides methods and wrappers around system methods for presenting a simple user interface (setup wizard).

    TODO: This Class only uses a bit of the advanced SwingAdvancedControlInterface Class. We should separate both.
